                        %li Mondays and Tuesdays 8:30 AM - 10:00 AM
                        %li Wednesdays and Thursdays 9:40 AM - 11:10 AM
                    %li Helping to serve lunch from 11:10 AM - 1:10 PM one to five days per week.
                    %li Riding the bus home with our students for 30-45 minutes at 4:00 PM one to five days per week.
                    %li Providing Administrative Assistance support on a flexible schedule throughout the week.
